Hi,
I have a question about using the mixmaster. I'm trying to use its 
reaction path feature. Therefore I want to load a csv-file with some 
data from a simulation with the H2O2Ar-mechanism. I created a file as 
described in the mixmaster-documentation. The first three lines are 
given in the appendix of this mail. Unfortunately there comes up 
always an error while loading the file. If anybody can tell me why 
it's going wrong please let me know.
Regards
   Albrecht
